      "comment_id" : 16534147,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "In most cases one needs to keep the original set, so in order to use <code>retainAll</code> it&#39;s necessary to make a copy of the original set. Then it&#39;s more efficient to use <code>HashSet</code> as suggested by <a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/a/8708783/1333025\">Z&#233;ychin</a> ."
    }, {
