    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<h1><code>Stream::anyMatch</code></h1>\n\n<p>Since Java 8 you could use <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/11/docs/api/java.base/java/util/stream/Stream.html#anyMatch(java.util.function.Predicate)\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>Stream::anyMatch</code></a>. </p>\n\n<pre><code>setA.stream().anyMatch(setB::contains)\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
