    "last_activity_date" : 1484664234,
    "creation_date" : 1484664234,
    "answer_id" : 41700001,
    "question_id" : 8708542,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I use  <em>org.apache.commons.collections.CollectionUtils</em></p>\n\n<pre><code>CollectionUtils.containsAny(someCollection1, someCollection2)\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>That is All!</strong>\nReturns <strong>true</strong> if at least one element is in both collections.</p>\n\n<p>Simple to use, and the name of the function is more suggestive.</p>\n"
  } ],
